{"tid":673661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳獲美撤銷售禁令 中興通訊:消息屬實","createTime":"2018-05-22T04:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T05:51:40.000Z","uid":54870,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c8d03302e97cd47d90c7230881d32e0b9bf71c","tid":673661,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"對於有內地傳媒引述消息報道，美國將取消中興通訊(00763)的銷售禁令，中興回應《每日經濟新聞》稱，消息屬實。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，美中就解決中興通訊相關爭端大致達成一致，美國將取消中興通訊銷售禁令，根據討論的協定維持其業務。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指出，中興通訊將被要求大規模調整管理層和董事會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-china-agree-on-broad-outline-to-settle-zte-controversy-1526959695\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fu-s-china-agree-on-broad-outline-to-settle-zte-controversy-1526959695&d=odoMKt4dcH3os18d4Fupb7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=47691c06\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-china-agree-on-broad-outline-to-settle-zte-controversy-1526959695</a>"},{"pid":"64a6aa4f55a9792c5667e030a2044e80e9b3a423","tid":673661,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac1aa8f2c494933ba09c215e6af7290bb76cacb8","tid":673661,"uid":120715,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"簽完不平等條約, 咪俾返jetso你囉"},{"pid":"94af0cc92106886ae2610a09adad17968b002d87","tid":673661,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:51:53.000Z","msg":"以後比老美揀住春袋做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d568f4c314a98418f488af3bf47a66eef9202e","tid":673661,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對於有內地傳媒引述消息報道</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n此post已完<br />\n<br />\n白宮自己出消息先信 (再屌)"},{"pid":"82dea285d1c6fb15c73160c3d1327c8196c8e33d","tid":673661,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"